    //   4. Try to import DD File with rejected lines.
    // 
    // TFS ID = 91091
    // Covers Test cases:
    // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    // Test Function Name                                                                       TFS ID
    // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    // LaunchLSVImportDirectDebitFile                                                            91091

